         Extended length of DOTs will equal more damage.  I do not know what the rationale is for saying otherwise.  I have read that comment on various boards and it always stands without any explanation.  You cannot seriously believe that it means DOTs will do the same damage over an extended period of time.  That would be a nerf.</P><P>However, I do believe that there is a good point to be discussed concerning efficiency.  This came to my mind immediately.  Timing!  Timing is everything for a necro just like it is for a ENC.  I know exactly when my Dark is going to wear off.  I never know if it is extended by the focus item so I wont take the chance, I will recast.  On the other hand, if it does extend the time and damage of the rest of my DoTs, I do not really care about their lengths.  I wait to recast after I receive the message.</P><P>53rd Heretic of Misty Knight (Tholluxe Paels)<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
