        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Dot stacking does need to be fixed. Adding to the length of the dots and decreasing the mana is very close to the same thing. Longer duration = less recast = less mana. However, more damage does not figure into that anywhere.  There needs to be either a) a separate focus effect, which would create even more problems when trying to pick out gear (unless of course they add more that 1 to items, heh), or b) change longer duration to increased damage/tic.</P><P><BR>Shauku Duskmaster<BR>I've got a nine<BR>A sign<BR>A set<BR>And now I've got a name.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
